{"tid":1942484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"莫乃光接公務員投訴　稱大部分部門仍每周3至4日工作","createTime":"2020-03-25T05:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T03:01:15.000Z","uid":240250,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7d7776bf45a299cb9e2959ba46d96f44ee6c523a","tid":1942484,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"政府早前宣布恢復公務員在家工作安排。立法會資訊科技界議員莫乃光說，接到不少公務員投訴，表示與上一輪在家工作安排並非一致，大部分部門仍維持3或4日工作。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，灣仔胡忠大廈有人確診，大廈有衞生署、教育局及通訊事務管理局等政府部門辦公室，絕大部分員工未有全面的在家工作安排，他批評有關做法令員工感到焦慮，希望政府能以員工的個人健康為首要考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516708-20200325.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516708-20200325.htm&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=8c3e52a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516708-20200325.htm&h=263be1ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516708-20200325.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n戇撚鳩今次真係返得多過二月好多，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28eedf84398233790e9b266efa426cc4a11e0ec1","tid":1942484,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T06:06:47.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"a3e4419972ea165bcfaa9e67d467975c2509a1af","tid":1942484,"uid":317378,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"咁慘，要唔要申請過黎，我地呢邊返足五日再ot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de8a83c573f57b44017f077e94ea878850eeacd","tid":1942484,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3e4419972ea165bcfaa9e67d467975c2509a1af","tid":1942484,"uid":317378,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"咁慘，要唔要申請過黎，我地呢邊返足五日再ot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T06:3